{"tid":2302400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署師召集！！國泰工會要人！！！","createTime":"2020-11-27T05:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T06:04:30.000Z","uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48c75079813f83b2f8616642b7790328ff971385","tid":2302400,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"聯署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePtvc45M7O6znuBZwo2_HHDe-lY-M2oNlOWYRt3N5ynq-wMg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSePtvc45M7O6znuBZwo2_HHDe-lY-M2oNlOWYRt3N5ynq-wMg%2Fviewform&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=98377a90\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePtvc45M7O6znuBZwo2_HHDe-lY-M2oNlOWYRt3N5ynq-wMg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2wHsGc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2wHsGc.jpg&h=99e75648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰空中服務員工會於《蘋果》刊登A1頭版廣告<br />\n以<span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"x-large\">「國泰打壓工會」</span></span>為標題<br />\n<br />\n當中寫上<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\">「工會抗爭，只因工人都是命運共同體」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n亦列出三個管理層的<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「惡行」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n包括<span class=\"pink\">滅絕年終談判、殲滅香港集體談判權以及損害勞工權益</span><br />\n並呼籲所有港人關注今次事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">今日國泰，明日全香港打工仔<br />\n已經有不少公司跟隨惡晒做法壓榨員工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足花一分鐘時間簽左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4398fdb23efbb5455fbdf5d1f30fe852965114","tid":2302400,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"聯署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePtvc45M7O6znuBZwo2_HHDe-lY-M2oNlOWYRt3N5ynq-wMg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https